et al. (2004), Jacobsen &amp; DuPlessis (1976), Jones (1971), Korine (2016), Korine et al. (2004), Kwiecinski &amp; Griffiths (1999), Penzhorn &amp; Rautenbach (1988), Tracy et al. (2007), Waters &amp; Vollrath (2003).
</paragraph>
